Description: AWS development standards
Pattern: **/src/**/*.py

AWS development requirements:
- Use IAM roles for authentication
- No hardcoded credentials
- Use AWS Secrets Manager or Parameter Store
- Use session objects for AWS clients
- Mock AWS services in tests using moto
- Use Infrastructure as Code (Terraform/CDK) 